<h2 class="p1">Structured content</h2>
<p class="p1"><a href="http://karenmcgrane.com/about/">Karen McGrane</a> delivered a provocative take on the current state of WYSIWYG, the pros and cons of in-place editing and the importance of structured content, a topic close to our content strategist's hearts.</p>
